          "reviewTitle": "Best Foundation Hands Down Beautiful Finish",
          "reviewText": "Hands down the best foundation I have ever used, and I have bought them all. It\u2019s moisture rich and gives a natural fresh finish. I have dry and mature skin, and get compliments daily when I use this. I love that a sunscreen is part of the formula and the color match is perfect. I hope they never stop making it. A bottle last a longtime and I find one or two pumps max is needed and application with my ring finger works best. I just slowly apply with a tapping and blend motion. It\u2019s buildable coverage and I set mine with a setting spray before adding blush or anything else. I don\u2019t find to be sticky, never irritates my sensitive skin, and the texture is smooth and doesn\u2019t oxidize is a bad way that many do. I have only used the same color match as my skin tone and can\u2019t speak to what a shade darker will look like. Highly recommend!",
